.fr-cs-ok { background: var(--callout-ok-bg, #e8f5e9); border-left: 3px solid var(--callout-ok, #4caf50); padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.fr-cs-ok ul { padding-left: 1.4em; margin: 8px 0 0; }
</style>
<div class="fr-cs-ok">
  <strong>Code Simplification: Clean</strong> — no findings across all three lenses.
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Reuse:</strong> No existing utilities to reuse — this is the foundation scaffold</li>
    <li><strong>Quality:</strong> No redundant state, no copy-paste patterns, no dead code</li>
